svg.text: All of our trips are designed for the beginner to the intermediate skill levels. The costs you see listed include
transportation, food, leadership, and equipment as needed. If you see a trip or program you think would be
fun for a private trip, that can be arranged as well! Feel free to contact us at 540-231-4982.

svg.text: Venture Out trips rely on safe and competent outdoor leaders. The trip leader training program offers formal
training focused on outdoor leadership and technical and interpersonal skills. Being a Venture Out leader is
about helping others discover and enjoy the great outdoors.
If you are interested in developing new skills, meeting new people, and working outside, then Venture
Out has a great student leadership opportunity for you. The success of Venture Out trips is directly
related to its trip leading staff. Venture Out currently offers multiple levels of training. First you may
become a trip leader candidate. If you show motivation, work ethic and traits of an outdoor leader,
you may be asked to become a leader in training. All Venture Out leaders and leaders-in-training must

svg.text: Venture Out is a unit within Recreational Sports that provides fun, safe, and educational outdoor services to
the students, faculty, staff, and community of Blacksburg. We specialize in exciting outdoor adventures, quality
rental gear at unbeatable rates, and valuable resources to help you plan the perfect adventure.
Venture Out offers extensive outdoor resources on local, regional, and national recreation opportunities.
We have a variety of brochures and books on hiking, backpacking, and camping in the New River Valley
including information on all of the Virginia State Parks and National Forest.
Venture Out's knowledgeable staff can provide you with personal advice to help you with your next adventure.
Let Venture Out be your link to the outdoors!
